      <title>印度高级官员称创纪录减税将刺激经济反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/india-s-growth-slowdown-temporary-chief-economic-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员表示，印度经济增长放缓是暂时的，预算中宣布的创纪录减税措施将有助于刺激消费并改善世界第五大经济体的私人投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/india-s-growth-slowdown-temporary-chief-economic-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 04:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
